		"description": "<p>Water genasi, also called undines, are born in places where elemental water makes its magic known. You gain the following benefits:</p>\n<p><strong>Aquatic. </strong>You can breathe both air and water. You gain a swim speed of 30 feet.</p>\n<p><strong>Aquatic Damage Versatility. </strong>Whenever you cast an acid or cold spell, you can switch one of these damage types out for the other.</p>\n<p><strong>Water Magic. </strong>You know the acid splash cantrip. Once you reach 3rd level, you can cast create or destroy wateronce per long rest. Your spellcasting ability for these spells is your choice of Constitution, Intelligence, Wisdom, or Charisma.</p>",
